  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Investigation in 3 steps the transition of young people with chronic diseases. FIRST STEP:
      qualitative survey. Interviews with carers, young people and parents. Chronic Diseases
      studied: epilepsy, HIV, sickle cell disease, obesity. SECOND STEP: Delphi consensus survey.
      Vote on internet : carers, patients' associations, young people and family. Chronic Diseases
      studied: all. THIRD STEP: validation survey. Vote on internet : young people. Chronic
      Diseases studied: all.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
